---
import "@splidejs/splide/css";
import { Splide, SplideSlide } from "astro-splide";
import type { Splide as SplideInterface } from "@splidejs/splide";
---

<Splide
  options={{
    perPage: 2,
    breakpoints: {
      640: {
        perPage: 1,
      },
    },
    rewind: true,
    gap: "1rem",
    autoplay: true, // ✅ Enables auto sliding
    interval: 2000, // ✅ Time between slides (in ms)
    pauseOnHover: true, // ✅ Optional: pause when hovered
    type: "loop", // ✅ Optional: loop continuously
    rewind: true,
    gap: "1rem",
  }}
  aria-labelledby="basic-example-heading"
  onMoved={(
    splide: SplideInterface,
    index: number,
    prev: number,
    dest: number
  ) => {
    console.log("splide:", splide);
  }}
>
  <SplideSlide>
    <figure class="bg-gray-100 p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md max-w-xl mx-auto">
      <blockquote class="text-lg italic text-gray-800">
        “Jenny is truly exceptional. Not only was the massage itself absolutely
        fantastic, but she also took the time to explain so much about facial
        massage and its benefits. Her knowledge is remarkable, yet what touched
        me the most is her warm personality and wisdom. The psychological lesson
        she gave me after our session is something I will never forget. I feel
        very grateful for the experience and I look forward to seeing her again
        very soon.”
      </blockquote>
    </figure>
  </SplideSlide>

  <SplideSlide>
    <figure class="bg-gray-100 p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md max-w-xl mx-auto">
      <blockquote class="text-lg italic text-gray-800">
        “I feel so lucky to have found Jenny! Originally I was only searching
        for a professional well trained mobile masseuse... then only to discover
        Jenny can also provide a full beauty service! Jenny was so easy to
        communicate and organise our home appointment with. I ended up adding an
        eyebrow shape, lash tint and lift... it's been along long time since I
        have been so happy with a result! Jenny will be my first call after
        booking flights. Her massage style is very unique... for me the perfect
        balance of tension release and relaxation... exactly what I asked for!
        Selfishly I am dreading others discovering her as she will be in high
        demand... but her approach, skills and expertise are too good not to
        share with others to experience. Jenny thank you and I'll be seeing you
        again soon!.”
      </blockquote>
    </figure>
  </SplideSlide>

  <SplideSlide>
    <figure class="bg-gray-100 p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md max-w-xl mx-auto">
      <blockquote class="text-lg italic text-gray-800">
        “I've had the pleasure of receiving various home treatments from Jenny
        including masssge, facials, waxing and eyelashes. As well as being a
        beautiful soul and a joy to deal with, Jenny is very, very good at her
        craft... experienced and very professional. I have had many massages and
        beauty treatments throughout the years and can honestly say Jenny is up
        there as one of the best.”
      </blockquote>
    </figure>
  </SplideSlide>

  <SplideSlide>
    <figure class="bg-gray-100 p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md max-w-xl mx-auto">
      <blockquote class="text-lg italic text-gray-800">
        “This spa experience was absolutely transformative. I’ve never felt so
        relaxed and rejuvenated.”
      </blockquote>
    </figure>
  </SplideSlide>
</Splide>
